# SmoothAir environment — everything is optional; the app runs keyless.

# Feedback storage on Vercel (serverless has no persistent disk).
# This Upstash Redis pair is the project's SINGLE permitted credential
# (see prompts/00-context.md). Without it, feedback uses a local JSON file
# on persistent hosts, or degrades to a friendly notice on Vercel.
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=

# Static key for GET /api/feedback/export?key=… (keeps crawlers out).
# Unset = export is open (fine for local dev).
# FEEDBACK_EXPORT_KEY=
